### Files to MODIFY
| File | Change |
|------|--------|
| `packages/server/src/request-relay.ts` | Add `usageTracker.record()` after successful relay |
| `packages/server/src/server.ts` | Initialize UsageTracker, serve dashboard static files, flush on shutdown |
